comment:
* Interface for clients of {@link SharedConnectivityManager} to register for changes in network
 * status.
 *
 * @hide

methods.name: void onHotspotNetworksUpdated(@NonNull List<HotspotNetwork> networks)
methods.comment:
* This method is being called by {@link SharedConnectivityService} to notify of a change in the
     * list of available Hotspot Networks.
     *
     * @param networks Updated Hotspot Network list.

methods.name: void onKnownNetworksUpdated(@NonNull List<KnownNetwork> networks)
methods.comment:
* This method is being called by {@link SharedConnectivityService} to notify of a change in the
     * list of available Known Networks.
     *
     * @param networks Updated Known Network list.

methods.name: void onSharedConnectivitySettingsChanged(@NonNull SharedConnectivitySettingsState state)
methods.comment:
* This method is being called by {@link SharedConnectivityService} to notify of a change in the
     * state of share connectivity settings.
     *
     * @param state The new state.

methods.name: void onHotspotNetworkConnectionStatusChanged(@NonNull HotspotNetworkConnectionStatus status)
methods.comment:
* This method is being called by {@link SharedConnectivityService} to notify of a change in the
     * status of the current hotspot network connection.
     *
     * @param status The new status.

methods.name: void onKnownNetworkConnectionStatusChanged(@NonNull KnownNetworkConnectionStatus status)
methods.comment:
* This method is being called by {@link SharedConnectivityService} to notify of a change in the
     * status of the current known network connection.
     *
     * @param status The new status.

methods.name: void onServiceConnected()
methods.comment: * This method is being called when the service is ready to be used.

methods.name: void onServiceDisconnected()
methods.comment: * This method is being called when the service is no longer available.

methods.name: void onRegisterCallbackFailed(@NonNull Exception exception)
methods.comment:
* This method is called when the registration of the callback with the shared connectivity
     * service failed.
     *
     * @param exception The exception received from the system when trying to connect to the
     *                  service.
